symphonyPotatoChips = Interpret.create(name: "Symphony Potato Chips", image_url: "https://i.imgur.com/s6yh1pG.png", website_url: "https://symphonychips.com/", description: "We began as a spice company! My dad Andre' Anderson is a retired Chef that worked on the famous Las Vegas Strip. While on the strip, he developed a custom blend that was sought after by patrons and fellow chefs alike. So naturally, when I tried it I was blown away! So much so that I convinced my dad that we needed to package and sell this ASAP! However, once we were featured in a grocery store we quickly learned that no one buys spices they cannot taste, no matter how pretty the package. So we begin doing in-store demonstrations! We started out by putting the spice on raw vegetables and popcorn. But it wasn't until we began putting it on homemade potato chips in the store did people begin to take notice. The feedback was the same, 'The spices are good, BUT WHERE CAN I GET A BAG OF THESE CHIPS!' So we had to listen to our customers and that's how Symphony Chips was born!", tag: "Food")

mayasCookies = Interpret.create(name: "Maya's Cookies", image_url: "https://i.imgur.com/wxxWdYm.jpg",  website_url: "https://www.mayascookies.com/", description: " Maya's cookies are so delicious because I use only the finest organic, premium whole food ingredients. These cookies are made in small batches and mixed by hand for a genuine homemade taste. I am proud to say that Maya's Cookies are 100% plant based, dairy free and cruelty free.  You are going to LOVE them!", tag: "Food")

projectPop = Interpret.create(name: "Project Pop", image_url: "https://i.imgur.com/4E20ylw.jpg", website_url: "https://www.eatprojectpop.com/", description: "A wild idea turned into a batch of popcorn. A batch of popcorn turned into a passion.  Shortly thereafter, all roads led to every batch of my signature Kettle Popcorn featuring ingredients that were organic, non-GMO, vegan and super easy to pronounce.  Project Pop is on a mission to give the gift of quality snacks, food education and smiles to snackers all over the globe.", tag: "Food")

veganSmart = Interpret.create(name: "Vegan Smart", image_url: "https://i.imgur.com/AoXUQmH.png", website_url: "https://www.vegansmart.com/", description: "In 2002, Kareem and Claude moved to Los Angeles. They immediately recognized the child obesity crisis and decided it was finally time to do something. They founded Healthy Body Products, a healthy vending machine company with the mission of providing healthier options to public schools. Within a year of moving to LA, they co-led a movement that resulted in a ban on junk food in the Los Angeles public schools. Within two years, they were awarded the contract for every public high school and middle school in Los Angeles. Their work garnered them an invitation from President Clinton and Governor Huckabee to visit their foundation and discuss their success in LA in hopes of rolling the ban out nationwide.", tag: "Food")

hellaNuts = Interpret.create(name: "Hella Nuts", image_url: "https://i.imgur.com/DatLUq6.jpg", website_url: "https://thatshellanuts.com/", description: "Hella Nuts™ patent-pending nut meat resembles ground meat. It can be used for tacos, pasta, plant-based burgers, shepards pie, pizzas, burrittos, stuffed bell peppers and an array of other dishes.", tag: "Food")

fineappleVegan = Interpret.create(name: "Fineapplevegan", image_url: "https://i.imgur.com/hxdlONj.png", website_url: "https://fineapplevegan.com/", description: "I find that people often connect through the enjoyment of food. So why not use ridiculously delicious, healthy and cruelty free food to do just that?! Not only do I want to bring people together, but my MAIN focus is to also show them that being vegan doesn't mean you have to sacrifice FLAVOR nor does it mean you have to eat grass all day. I put my EVERYTHING into each and every dish that I prepare. I spend hours, if not days, to perfect each spice, flavor, texture until I get it right. This is more than just vegan food. This is a lifestyle. Whether you're already vegan or a curious carnivore, all are welcome! I promise, you won't regret using one of my BOMB recipes for your 'Meatless Monday' meals!", tag: "Food")

tubbysTaste = Interpret.create(name: "Tubby's Taste", image_url: "https://i.imgur.com/1CnJn6v.png", website_url: "https://www.tubbystaste.com/", description: "Tubby’s Taste is a vegan cookie company inspired by our Founder’s Jamaican-American Roots", tag: "Food")


p "#{Interpret.count} interpret(s) out of 7 foods created"

